text: Nicoletta Abbate is an Italian water polo player. She was a member of the Italian women's national water polo team. She played at the 1989 European Water Polo Championship, 1991 European Water Polo Championship, and 1994 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Giulia segna sempre yellowball.it Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Italian water polo players
